type": "APP_IMG_HERO", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974466_2055286774822209_4338361723960595313_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=rgR6RMTH0-8Q7kNvgFQ2o_Y&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYC1-L55b-WX5hR8u27wNuuGis8Je6JRLMAHO-fvpDx6uQ&oe=670E58A7"}, {"file_name": "Fluent XR Cover Art.png", "id": "678364797690874", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974640_678364801024207_2897138990588590099_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=1GGn6m_ntYAQ7kNvgGVP1hb&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAqo4HlLyy3OBiY2_8PeCS0Tf69XXNoV0DBgSwTxBKAPA&oe=670E5EAB"}, {"file_name": "Fluent XR Logo transparent.png", "id": "212845385153628", "image_type": "APP_IMG_LOGO_TRANSPARENT", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974821_212845391820294_4065972029516719811_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=wZbAD5FHQAMQ7kNvgE-wPvR&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCBwgM7u45gUTLi_BTb6qlLkGOrVSJrI9YCT57hdXTIxA&oe=670E43D6"}]}, "id": "1137501624009601", "locale": "en_GB", "screenshots": [], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "FluentXR", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Unlock a personalized language learning journey with FluentXR. Using mixed reality passthrough technology, FluentXR transforms your home into an interactive learning space. \n\nStep into a realm where learning is not just fun and effective, but also deeply personalized. FluentXR is not just another language learning app; it's your own private linguistics lab. \n\nTag real-world objects in your space with text and audio labels, making learning immersive and contextually relevant. Dive into our Word Shuffle mini-game to reinforce your skills and beat the timer. \n\nCurrent Features:\nTagging Language: English\nLearning Language: French\nMini-Game: Word Shuffle\n470+ available tags geared towards common living room objects such as \u201cCouch\u201d, \u201cTelevision\u201d, and \u201cGaming Console\u201d\n\nFluentXR is an ever-evolving platform, continually expanding its selection of languages and mini-games. Achieve language mastery with FluentXR\u2014where your home becomes your classroom.", "short_description": "Transform your language learning experience.\n\nUtilizing mixed-reality passthrough technology turn your home into a dynamic classroom. Tag real-world objects in your living room with 470+ customizable tags for learning French. Sharpen your skills through the Word Shuffle mini-game.\n\nFluentXR is an ever-evolving platform, updating with new languages and interactive mini-games. Dive into a context-rich home environment that's both captivating and practical."}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "Fluent XR Cover Art - Portrait.png", "id": "6647755272010080", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_PORTRAIT", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982588_6647755275343413_6975862371154701560_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=V3EHO67dcOMQ7kNvgGCwroH&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBMjVKPcCjZtX1c6frsN74TX3f84PjRuMzZEq4aXymLKw&oe=670E6CB4"}, {"file_name": "Fluent XR Mobile Icon.png", "id": "2082304598777986", "image_type": "APP_IMG_ICON", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974858_2082304602111319_6670855186104070571_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=6Q5Fu8R9I40Q7kNvgGvublK&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYABsczbf16KdBGRLwSO8q0cpklR2ZBEr1vepbGhwQCLWA&oe=670E55AC"}, {"file_name": "Fluent XR Logo transparent.png", "id": "1984998648546806", "image_type": "APP_IMG_LOGO_TRANSPARENT", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982562_1984998651880139_3178193652368604560_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=n0u1pIygHO8Q7kNvgHa-7KK&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAYbJEXPryrIvcf-7jcTOIG69x4Su_p7G1B3TtpTlXk1g&oe=670E490E"}, {"file_name": "Fluent XR Cover Art.png", "id": "1753372745086018", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974868_1753372748419351_7413283912851125343_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=p2_Y3hG8LQcQ7kNvgGoBL1B&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBMtw4GPka8dGdBlFYEDgRMziVEu3GGTxoO8vjgBLo2xw&oe=670E5E75"}, {"file_name": "Fluent XR Cover Art - Square.png", "id": "1307619323205125", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_SQUARE", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75334061_1307619326538458_7751189323196005702_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=NhRMuPZAw6YQ7kNvgGyfrRe&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCnGXkJDPT5rDRY71A9s6Lil7YzcRgwQTR2NpNe3mZ6CQ&oe=670E3CB4"}, {"file_name": "Fluent XR Cover Art - Mini Landscape.png", "id": "1239723750053984", "image_type": "APP_IMG_SMALL_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75230044_1239723753387317_7790772509280140276_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=UO-5REmtIC8Q7kNvgF-5xdr&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDQeF_OEM4iNv5l6GDCkW3wCAZWyRWzQGB9l3j8LCw6HQ&oe=670E609E"}, {"file_name": "Fluent XR PDP Art.png", "id": "1061096168226207", "image_type": "APP_IMG_HERO", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75340707_1061096171559540_9065798130022169599_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=iB0_Xl6F5jMQ7kNvgHMxdWz&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYB7KT1h29y-q8I8FCeXRYxbh9PgWckU8iGCA1MclEdjIg&oe=670E6D73"}]}, "id": "449609844722656", "locale": "en_US", "screenshots": [{"file_name": "Sequence 04.00_27_46_18.Still011.png", "id": "755435526614104", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39003240_755435529947437_3157283510711493706_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=zqy2f5OX1gYQ7kNvgHipitR&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCI9_FEHlEJJB8fRdQki-ev-VaoxFfyCVr1yXOn4473cQ&oe=670E5ABF"}, {"file_name": "Sequence 04.00_34_53_09.Still016.png", "id": "377326888090872", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031365_377326891424205_2576812618867292544_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=JkPRGW_wi8oQ7kNvgHcE-U3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBmZE7l9R-ArT8GTXhCsHL5fKCRMMeGPycCUvVyOB2AZg&oe=670E5C8E"}, {"file_name": "Sequence 04.00_49_22_19.Still025.png", "id": "1792607307852843", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39035387_1792607311186176_5280458374548206595_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=gEg9ePyo6HkQ7kNvgE7i5p5&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYB1QKCSN_rnwUjek8Sd4uEBMhEcwOmMTuR9dxJn1ZVZpw&oe=670E6196"}, {"file_name": "Sequence 04.00_52_56_05.Still030.png", "id": "245249301718520", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031325_245249305051853_1598234300064219875_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=hT71QSoZWuAQ7kNvgGU-nJ3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAq__iUKN5zzO7cET1b2uOj9SSWN4IH-YNYA0MDb2Ginw&oe=670E4137"}, {"file_name": "Sequence 04.00_11_37_00.Still002.png", "id": "733795254815172", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39036675_733795258148505_1346935370172344005_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=sNvPxOgSoSQQ7kNvgG0_Yht&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYATPQCdXcd0ljBfmAnot348N29dwlXGBW9FZnTz3RXuJA&oe=670E4872"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "Sequence 04.00_27_46_18.Still011.png", "id": "894248482404839", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974686_894248485738172_2991357501924730672_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=ULkx2Vzmf3MQ7kNvgGbj6FZ&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYChMZ7DvvAcBO5ftI4VOlm6BP7gKgUV05FvQJl5FuJFTQ&oe=670E601B"}, "display_name": "FluentXR", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Unlock a personalized language learning journey through your mixed reality home. FluentXR transforms your space into an interactive learning environment.\n\nStep into a realm where learning is not just fun and effective, but also deeply personalized. FluentXR is not just another language learning app; it's your own private linguistics lab.\n\nTag real-world objects in your space with text and audio labels, making learning immersive and contextually relevant. Dive into our Word Shuffle mini-game to reinforce your skills and challenge yourself using the timer.\n\nCurrent Features:\nSpace: Living Room\nMain Language: English\nLearning: French / fran\u00e7ais\nMini-Game: Word Shuffle\n470+ available tags geared towards common living room objects such as \u201cCouch\u201d, \u201cTelevision\u201d, \u201cChess Set\u201d and \u201cGaming Console\u201d\n\nFluentXR is an ever-evolving platform, continually expanding its selection of languages, locations, and mini-games. Achieve language mastery with FluentXR\u2014where your home becomes your classroom.\n\nNext Expansion: \nSpace: Kitchen\nSpace: Bedroom\nMain Language: French\nLearning Language: Spanish / espa\u00f1ol \nLearning Language: English\nMini-Game: Sentence Scramble", "short_description": "Transform your language learning experience. \n\nUtilizing mixed-reality passthrough technology turn your home into a dynamic classroom. Tag real-world objects in your living room with 470+ customizable tags for learning French. Sharpen your skills through the Word Shuffle mini-game.\n\nFluentXR is an ever-evolving platform, updating with new languages, locations, and interactive mini-games. Dive into a context-rich home environment that's both captivating and practical."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://zenfri.ca/fluentxr-privacy-policy/", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "ZenFri Inc.", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://zenfri.ca/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": null, "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "362692211442873"